							"gravatarHash":"74ee2eb74c2e385593a4d91a26a785e4",
							"avatar128":"/avatar-redirect/3e71b0bb-d5ea-4ce9-ac04-7d822fd3c245/128/",
							"aboutMe":"I'm a Blender Materials Creator & Pixel/Voxel Art enthusiast, constantly learning & enhancing my skills. Passionate about sharing knowledge (Yokoten - \u6a2a \u5c55). Let's collaborate & create something amazing together!\r\n\r\nGamer Tag: Dr. Hacker \"BE HACK 2000\"",
							"aboutMeUrl":"https://sketchfab.com/codigopixel/collections",
							"fullName":"Paco Salas",
							"socialNetworks":[]
						},
						"name":"Diamond 03",
						"displayName":"Diamond 03",
						"description":"Welcome to the shimmering world of diamond texture material! This magnificent material is like having a piece of the galaxy in your hands. The reflective surface looks like a million tiny stars were trapped inside and trying to escape. Its fully procedural design means that every diamond texture is unique, with a base color that can be adjusted to your heart's content. You can choose from a wide range of reflection colors that resemble the purest crystal water, a rainbow after a storm, or even a unicorn's mane. The IOR control allows you to change the refractive index of the material, making the diamonds appear even more realistic. And with the reflection factor, you can control how much light is reflected, making this material perfect for anything from a subtle accent to an eye-catching centerpiece. So, let your imagination run wild and create your very own dazzling world with diamond texture material!",
						"assetType":"material",
						"category":"glass",
